description: Cooper Noriega's body was found in a Burbank parking lot on Thursday evening and pronounced dead at the scene. Four days before his death, Noriega announced on social media that he was creating a Discord server dedicated to discussing mental health, which he invited his followers to join.  Shortly before his death, he posted a video on TikTok, where he has over 1.7 million followers, with the caption, "Who else b thinking they gon die young af."
